 the Yuan dynasty who had demanded tribute. * {{ill|Keichō|ja|Keichō|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1600|ja|1600|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 13|ja|10月13日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – A siege was launched against Ōtsu Castle (the Battle of Ōtsu Castle). * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1872|ja|1872|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 9|ja|10月9日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – A telegraph line was opened between Tokyo and Kyoto.
