ft}} {{ill|1751|ja|1751|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 25|ja|10月25日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Namiki Sōsuke|ja|並木宗輔|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a jōruri author (* {{ill|1695|ja|1695|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Bunka (era)|ja|文化 (元号)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 13rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1816|ja|1816|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 27|ja|10月27日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Yamato Kyōden|ja|山東京伝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a writer of popular fiction (* {{ill|1761|ja|1761|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
== Commemorations == * {{ill|Kajimayā Celebration|ja|カジマヤー祝い|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} – In Okinawa, a 97‐year‐old (by traditional count) longevity celebration is held in which a windmill (カジマヤー) is presented.
