* {{ill|Kansei|ja|Kansei|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 11th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1799|ja|1799|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 5|ja|10月5日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Minotsuku Genpo|ja|箕作阮甫|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a rangaku scholar († {{ill|1863|ja|1863|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
