{{Lunisolar September}} '''September 7''' is the 7th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September (Nagatsuki)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=draft|qq=draft}} day is {{ill|Senbu|ja|先負|qq=draft|qq=draft}} .
== Events == * {{ill|Chishō|ja|治承|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 4th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1180|ja|1180|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|September 27|ja|9月27日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – In Kiso, {{ill|Minamoto no Yoshinaka|ja|Minamoto no Yoshinaka|qq=draft|qq=draft}} raised an army to defeat the Heike. * {{ill|Kennin|ja|建仁|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 3rd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1203|ja|1203|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|October 13|ja|10月13日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – Minamoto no Sanetomo (renamed from his original name to {{ill|Minamoto no Sanemoto|ja|源実朝|lt=Sanemoto|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) was appointed as Seii Taishōgun. * {{ill|Kenchi|ja|Kenji|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1275|ja|1275|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|September 27|ja|9月27日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – The Kamakura shogunate’s regent, {{ill|Hōjō Tokimune|ja|北条時宗|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , executed five envoys from the Yuan dynasty who had demanded tribute. * {{ill|Keichō|ja|Keichō|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 5th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1600|ja|1600|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|October 13|ja|10月13日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – A siege was launched against Ōtsu Castle (the Battle of Ōtsu Castle). * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 5th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1872|ja|1872|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|October 9|ja|10月9日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – A telegraph line was opened between Tokyo and Kyoto.
== Births == * {{ill|Enryaku|ja|延暦|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 5th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|786|ja|786|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|October 3|ja|10月3日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – Emperor {{ill|Saga|ja|Emperor Saga|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , the 52nd emperor († {{ill|842|ja|842|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Eishō|ja|永正|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 8th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1511|ja|1511|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|September 28|ja|9月28日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – {{ill|Matsudaira Kiyoyasu|ja|松平清康|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , a Sengoku-period warrior and grandfather of {{ill|Tokugawa Ieyasu|ja|徳川家康|qq=draft|qq=draft}} († {{ill|1535|ja|1535|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Kansei|ja|Kansei|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 11th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1799|ja|1799|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|October 5|ja|10月5日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – {{ill|Minotsuku Genpo|ja|箕作阮甫|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , a rangaku scholar († {{ill|1863|ja|1863|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ).
