{{Lunisolar September}} 
'''September 7''' is the 7th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September (Nagatsuki)|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  day is {{ill|Senbu|ja|先負|qq=draft|qq=draft}} .

== Events ==
* {{ill|Chishō|ja|治承|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 4th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|1180|ja|1180|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|September 27|ja|9月27日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – In Kiso, {{ill|Minamoto no Yoshinaka|ja|Minamoto no Yoshinaka|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  raised an army to defeat the Heike.
* {{ill|Kennin|ja|建仁|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 3rd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|1203|ja|1203|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|October 13|ja|10月13日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – Minamoto no Sanetomo (renamed from his original name to {{ill|Minamoto no Sanemoto|ja|源実朝|lt=Sanemoto|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) was appointed as Seii Taishōgun.
* {{ill|Kenchi|ja|Kenji|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|1275|ja|1275|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|September 27|ja|9月27日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – The Kamakura shogunate’s regent, {{ill|Hōjō Tokimune|ja|北条時宗|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , executed five envoys from the Yuan dynasty who had demanded tribute.
* {{ill|Keichō|ja|Keichō|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 5th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|1600|ja|1600|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|October 13|ja|10月13日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – A siege was launched against Ōtsu Castle (the Battle of Ōtsu Castle).
* {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 5th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|1872|ja|1872|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|October 9|ja|10月9日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – A telegraph line was opened between Tokyo and Kyoto.

